{"title":"Boxing referee Frank Cappuccino dies aged 86","wikiTitle":"Boxing_referee_Frank_Cappuccino_dies_aged_86","wid":2212073,"lang":"en","namespace":"","integerNamespace":0,"timestamp":"2016-05-08T18:45:48Z","type":"ARTICLE","tables":[],"lists":[["TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://www.philly.com/philly/obituaries/20150610_Frank_Cappuccino__86__legendary_boxing_referee_for_50_years.html?c\u003dr, title\u003dFrank Cappuccino, 86, legendary boxing referee for 50 years, author\u003dJohn F. Morrison, pub\u003dPhiladelphia Media Network, date\u003dJune 10, 2015]","TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://www.worldboxingnews.net/2015/06/10/news/gatti-ward-i-referee-frank-cappuccino-mourned, title\u003dGatti-Ward I referee Frank Cappuccino mourned, author\u003d, pub\u003dworldboxingnews.net, date\u003dJune 10, 2015]","TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://espn.go.com/boxing/story/_/id/13045578/frank-cappuccino-legendary-boxing-referee-dies-86, title\u003dFrank Cappuccino, legendary boxing referee, dies at 86, author\u003dDan Rafael, pub\u003dESPN, date\u003dJune 9, 2015]"]],"links":[{"id":"boxing","description":"boxing"},{"id":"Pennsylvania","description":"Pennsylvania"}],"externalLinks":[],"sections":["Sources"],"paragraphs":["TEMPLATE[date, June 10, 2015] TEMPLATE[Sports] TEMPLATE[image, Al Pepper] Long-time boxing referee TEMPLATE[w, Frank Cappuccino] has died at the age of 86. Cappuccino, who died in TEMPLATE[w, Yardley, Pennsylvania, Yardley], Pennsylvania on Monday, was suffering from TEMPLATE[w, Alzheimer\u0027s disease]. He started his career in the 1950s and officiated on some of the most famous fights in boxing history; these included 94 world championship fights.","Pennsylvania State Athletic Commission executive director Greg Sirb paid tribute to Cappuccino. He said, in remarks to TEMPLATE[w, ESPN], \"When he was in his prime, there is no doubt he was one of the top five referees in the world. [...] When he was reffing, he was poetry in motion. He had as much respect from the fighters as any referee there is. I just think they liked his style. He was straightforward. When you got Frank Cappuccino assigned to your bout, you knew you made it.\"","Some of the most notable fights that Cappuccino officiated over include TEMPLATE[w, Lennox Lewis] vs. TEMPLATE[w, Shannon Briggs], TEMPLATE[w, Mike Tyson] vs. TEMPLATE[w, Michael Spinks], and the 2002 TEMPLATE[w, Ring magazine Fight of the Year, fight-of-the-year] between TEMPLATE[w, Micky Ward, Mike Ward] and TEMPLATE[w, Arturo Gatti]. He himself belonged to both the Pennsylvania and TEMPLATE[w, New Jersey] boxing halls of fame.","Cappuccino spoke openly about his friendship with notorious boxer Mike Tyson. He had said \"I can\u0027t say a bad thing about Mike Tyson[...] He\u0027s always been very good to me.\" Cappuccino was the referee during six of Tyson\u0027s fights, including his 91-second victory over Michael Spinks in 1998.","He refereed his last fight in 2008 and was a boxing judge up until 2010. He is survived by his wife, Florence.","TEMPLATE[haveyoursay]","TEMPLATE[Publish] TEMPLATE[Archive]"],"categories":[{"id":"Category:Sports","description":"Category:Sports"},{"id":"Category:Boxing","description":"Category:Boxing"},{"id":"Category:United_States","description":"Category:United States"},{"id":"Category:North_America","description":"Category:North America"},{"id":"Category:Pennsylvania","description":"Category:Pennsylvania"},{"id":"Category:Obituaries","description":"Category:Obituaries"},{"id":"Category:Mike_Smith_(Wikinewsie)","description":"Category:Mike Smith (Wikinewsie)"}],"templates":[{"name":"date","description":["June 10, 2015"]},{"name":"Sports","description":[]},{"name":"image","description":["Al Pepper"]},{"name":"w","description":["Frank Cappuccino"]},{"name":"w","description":["Yardley, Pennsylvania","Yardley"]},{"name":"w","description":["Alzheimer\u0027s disease"]},{"name":"w","description":["ESPN"]},{"name":"w","description":["Lennox Lewis"]},{"name":"w","description":["Shannon Briggs"]},{"name":"w","description":["Mike Tyson"]},{"name":"w","description":["Michael Spinks"]},{"name":"w","description":["Ring magazine Fight of the Year","fight-of-the-year"]},{"name":"w","description":["Micky Ward","Mike Ward"]},{"name":"w","description":["Arturo Gatti"]},{"name":"w","description":["New Jersey"]},{"name":"haveyoursay","description":[]},{"name":"source","description":["url\u003dhttp://www.philly.com/philly/obituaries/20150610_Frank_Cappuccino__86__legendary_boxing_referee_for_50_years.html?c\u003dr","title\u003dFrank Cappuccino, 86, legendary boxing referee for 50 years","author\u003dJohn F. Morrison","pub\u003dPhiladelphia Media Network","date\u003dJune 10, 2015"]},{"name":"source","description":["url\u003dhttp://www.worldboxingnews.net/2015/06/10/news/gatti-ward-i-referee-frank-cappuccino-mourned","title\u003dGatti-Ward I referee Frank Cappuccino mourned","author\u003d","pub\u003dworldboxingnews.net","date\u003dJune 10, 2015"]},{"name":"source","description":["url\u003dhttp://espn.go.com/boxing/story/_/id/13045578/frank-cappuccino-legendary-boxing-referee-dies-86","title\u003dFrank Cappuccino, legendary boxing referee, dies at 86","author\u003dDan Rafael","pub\u003dESPN","date\u003dJune 9, 2015"]},{"name":"Publish","description":[]},{"name":"Archive","description":[]}],"templatesSchema":["url","title","author","pub","date","url","title","author","pub","date","url","title","author","pub","date"],"highlights":[]}
{"title":"English actor Christopher Lee dies aged 93","wikiTitle":"English_actor_Christopher_Lee_dies_aged_93","wid":2216681,"lang":"en","namespace":"","integerNamespace":0,"timestamp":"2017-01-23T23:25:32Z","type":"ARTICLE","tables":[],"lists":[["TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://www.theguardian.com/film/2015/jun/11/christopher-lee-dies-at-the-age-of-93-dracula, title\u003dChristopher Lee dies at the age of 93, author\u003dBenjamin Lee, Hannah Ellis-Perersen, pub\u003dThe Guardian, date\u003dJune 12, 2015]","TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-33098353, title\u003dSir Christopher Lee: Screen legend dies aged 93, author\u003d, pub\u003dBBC News Online, date\u003dJune 12, 2015]","TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/christopher-lee-inside-his-secret-life-in-heavy-metal-20150611, title\u003dChristopher Lee: The Actor\u0027s Secret Life in Heavy Metal, author\u003dJon Weiderhorn, pub\u003dRolling Stone, date\u003dJune 11, 2015]","TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://www.avclub.com/article/rip-christopher-lee-220716, title\u003dR.I.P. Christopher Lee, author\u003dLara Unnerstall, pub\u003dThe A.V. Club, date\u003dJune 11, 2015]"]],"links":[{"id":"England","description":"English"},{"id":"heavy_metal","description":"heavy metal"}],"externalLinks":[],"sections":["Sources"],"paragraphs":["TEMPLATE[date, June 13, 2015] TEMPLATE[Culture_and_entertainment] TEMPLATE[image_credit, Avda] Famed English actor, singer and author TEMPLATE[w, Sir Christopher Lee] died last Sunday morning in TEMPLATE[w, London] aged 93, after being admitted to TEMPLATE[w, Chelsea and Westminster Hospital] for heart failure and respiratory problems. News of his death only became public on Thursday, as his wife of 54 years, Birgit KrÃ¸ncke Lee, wished first to inform friends and family.","A spokesman for the TEMPLATE[w, Royal Borough of Kensington and Chelsea] confirmed the issuing of his death certificate.","Lee first rose to prominence in the 1950s starring in TEMPLATE[w, Hammer Horror] films as the classic movie monsters TEMPLATE[w, Dracula] and TEMPLATE[w, Frankenstein\u0027s Monster, Frankenstein] and was more recently seen as TEMPLATE[w, Saruman the White] in the TEMPLATE[w, Lord of the Rings (film series), Lord of the Rings] and TEMPLATE[w, The Hobbit (film series), The Hobbit] films as well as portraying the villainous TEMPLATE[w, Count Dooku] in the TEMPLATE[w, Star Wars] films TEMPLATE[w, Star Wars Episode II: Attack of the Clones, Attack of the Clones] and TEMPLATE[w, Star Wars Episode III: Revenge of the Sith, Revenge of the Sith].","In 2010 Lee released a heavy metal album titled TEMPLATE[w, Charlemagne: By the Sword and the Cross] followed by another metal album in 2013, TEMPLATE[w, Charlemagne: The Omens of Death] and several collections of Heavy Metal cover songs including A Heavy Metal Christmas, A Heavy Metal Christmas Too and Metal Knight.","In 2008 Lee was TEMPLATE[w, Orders,_decorations, and medals of the United Kingdom, anchor\u003dKnighthood, knighted] for services to drama and charity, and in 2001 received a TEMPLATE[w, Bafta Fellowship].","Lee is survived by his wife Birgit and daughter Christina.","TEMPLATE[haveyoursay]","TEMPLATE[Publish] TEMPLATE[Archive]"],"categories":[{"id":"Category:England","description":"Category:England"},{"id":"Category:Culture_and_entertainment","description":"Category:Culture and entertainment"},{"id":"Category:Obituaries","description":"Category:Obituaries"},{"id":"Category:United_Kingdom","description":"Category:United Kingdom"},{"id":"Category:Europe","description":"Category:Europe"},{"id":"Category:Film","description":"Category:Film"},{"id":"Category:Music","description":"Category:Music"},{"id":"Category:Heavy_metal","description":"Category:Heavy metal"},{"id":"Category:Star_Wars","description":"Category:Star Wars"}],"templates":[{"name":"date","description":["June 13, 2015"]},{"name":"Culture_and_entertainment","description":[]},{"name":"image_credit"