{"title":"Francesc SolÃ© wins Andorra Ultra Trail again","wikiTitle":"Francesc_SolÃ©_wins_Andorra_Ultra_Trail_again","wid":2263401,"lang":"en","namespace":"","integerNamespace":0,"timestamp":"2015-07-28T17:30:38Z","type":"ARTICLE","tables":[],"lists":[["TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://crono.andorraultratrail.com/, title\u003dCrono Andorra Ultra Trail Vallnord (ranks \u0026 times), author\u003d, pub\u003dVallnord, date\u003dJuly 1, 2015 (date of access), lang\u003dCatalan]","TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://www.andorraultratrail.com/index.php?lang\u003den, title\u003dAndorra Ultra Trail Vallnord (startpage with data about tracks), author\u003d, pub\u003dVallnord, date\u003dJuly 1, 2015 (date of access)]","TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttps://www.lepape-info.com/running-2/courses/chaleur-et-record-de-participation-pour-landorra-ultra-trail-vallnord-2015-andorre/, title\u003dChaleur et record de participation pour lâAndorra Ultra Trail Vallnord 2015 (Andorre), author\u003dClÃ©ment Excoffier, pub\u003dLepape Info, date\u003dJune 30, 2015, lang\u003dFrench]","TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://www.regio7.cat/esports/2015/06/28/nuria-picas-vencedora-marato-dels/319740.html, title\u003dNÃºria Picas Ã©s la vencedora en la MaratÃ³ dels Cims amb la sortida i arribada a Ordino, author\u003d, pub\u003dRegiÃ³7, pubtarget\u003dca:RegiÃ³7, date\u003dJune 28, 2015, lang\u003dCatalan]","TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://www.bondia.ad/esports/mes-de-600-corredors-la-cursa-solidaria-de-landorra-ultra-trail, title\u003dMÃ©s de 600 corredors a la cursa solidÃ ria de lâAndorra Ultra Trail, author\u003d, pub\u003dBondia (newspaper), date\u003dJune 28, 2015, lang\u003dCatalan]","TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://www.diariandorra.ad/index.php?option\u003dcom_k2\u0026view\u003ditem\u0026id\u003d42206, title\u003dLâAndorra excursionista, author\u003dJordi Pasques, pub\u003dDiari d\u0027Andorra, date\u003dJune 27, 2015, lang\u003dCatalan]","TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://www.vamosacorrer.com/noticias/nuria-picas-y-francesc-sole-correran-la-andorra-ultra-trail-vallnord-2015-20150522.html, title\u003dNÃ¹ria Picas y Francesc SolÃ© correrÃ¡n la Andorra Ultra Trail Vallnord 2015, author\u003d@Eizquierdo68, pub\u003dEl Correo, date\u003dMay 25, 2015, 09:33, lang\u003dSpanish]"]],"links":[],"externalLinks":[],"sections":["Sources"],"paragraphs":["TEMPLATE[date, July 2, 2015]TEMPLATE[Sports] On Saturday, Francesc SolÃ© reached the finish in TEMPLATE[w, Ordino] as winner of the TEMPLATE[w, Andorra] TEMPLATE[w, ultramarathon, Ultra Trail] after 170 TEMPLATE[w, kilometre, km] over an altitude range of 13,500 TEMPLATE[w, metre, meters] and 31:09 hours.","Between 7am on Friday and 8am on Saturday, over 1600 competitors started in four races between single and quadruple TEMPLATE[w, marathon].","The Andorran Ultra Trail lead, for the seventh time now, on tracks through valleys, over passes and tops of the small country in the TEMPLATE[w, Pyrenees]. The first to arrive were the winners of Celestrail, a double marathon ranging over 5,000 meters of altitude, after a midnight start on Friday night. TEMPLATE[w, Marc Casal] made it in only 10:06:59, followed by Guillaume Beauxis with 10:35:29 and Nicolas Cerisier in 11:57:04. Olatx AlvariÃ±o won the women\u0027s competition in 13:28:45, well ahead of Sandra Castellanas at 14:51:17, and Eva Belles at 15:41:27.  TEMPLATE[translation_note, MaratÃ³, en, Catalan language, Marathon] \u0026mdash; 42.5km, 3,000m altitude  \u0026mdash; began at eight in the morning on Saturday with the first, TEMPLATE[w, Marc Pinsach], finishing in 4:35:12, and TEMPLATE[w, sister\u003dw:ca, NÃºria Picas] in 5:23:05. While winning the women\u0027s competition NÃºria Picas completed her series of four TEMPLATE[w, trail running, mountain marathons] within four weeks.","Then it was Francesc SolÃ© winning the main event TEMPLATE[translated_quote, en, Catalan language, Round the peaks, Ronda dels cims] \u0026mdash; 170km, 13,500m altitude \u0026mdash; in the outstanding time of 31:08:58. He was followed an hour later by JÃ©rÃ´me Lucas, 32:08:41; and Nahuel Passerat, 33:02:02.  Nerea MartÃ­nez reached the goal in the women\u0027s race in 38:47:44, overall 13th, and more than seven hours ahead of the second Irina Malejonock at 46:01:38, and Marta MuixÃ­ at 46:34:48. Finally 162 runners completed the race which makes about 45 percent of the 357 participants.","The TEMPLATE[translated_quote, en, Catalan language, Mythic, MÃ­tic] race over 112km and 9,700m started at 10pm on Friday; its winners were after 18:56:53 hours, Eduard BarcelÃ³, men; and, deep in the night, after 27:35:34 hours, Roser EspaÃ±ol, women. On places two and three followed Eva Zbornikova and AgnÃ¨s Francastel. Second in the men\u0027s race was Ion Azpiroz in front of Julien Jorro and Jordi Lopez who finished both together with the same time.","On Sunday more than 600 participants walked a solidary trail of 10km meant to include the less mobile. Finally, the last to cross the line was Eric Desgeorge on Sunday at nearly midnight after 64:39:08 hours. TEMPLATE[haveyoursay]","TEMPLATE[Publish] TEMPLATE[Archive]"],"categories":[{"id":"category:Sports","description":"category:Sports"},{"id":"Category:Andorra","description":"Category:Andorra"},{"id":"Category:Europe","description":"Category:Europe"},{"id":"Category:Spain","description":"Category:Spain"},{"id":"Category:France","description":"Category:France"}],"templates":[{"name":"date","description":["July 2, 2015"]},{"name":"Sports","description":[]},{"name":"w","description":["Ordino"]},{"name":"w","description":["Andorra"]},{"name":"w","description":["ultramarathon","Ultra Trail"]},{"name":"w","description":["kilometre","km"]},{"name":"w","description":["metre","meters"]},{"name":"w","description":["marathon"]},{"name":"w","description":["Pyrenees"]},{"name":"w","description":["Marc Casal"]},{"name":"translation_note","description":["MaratÃ³","en","Catalan language","Marathon"]},{"name":"w","descriptio