{"title":"C-130 Hercules crashes in Medan, Indonesia","wikiTitle":"C-130_Hercules_crashes_in_Medan,_Indonesia","wid":2273120,"lang":"en","namespace":"","integerNamespace":0,"timestamp":"2015-08-04T23:02:38Z","type":"ARTICLE","tables":[],"lists":[["TEMPLATE[wikinews, title\u003dAirAsia disaster: Bodies, wreckage found, date\u003dDecember 30, 2014]","TEMPLATE[wikinews, title\u003dAirAsia jet vanishes over Indonesia, 162 missing, date\u003dDecember 28, 2014]"],["TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-33339965, title\u003dIndonesia transport plane crash death toll rises, author\u003d, pub\u003dBBC News Online, date\u003dJuly 1, 2015]","TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://www.military.com/daily-news/2015/07/01/indonesia-c130-crash-death-toll-at-141-as-search-effort-ends.html, title\u003dIndonesia C-130 Crash Death Toll at 141 as Search Effort Ends, author\u003dNiniek Karmini ([[Associated Press, AP]]), pub\u003dMilitary.com, date\u003dJuly 1, 2015]","TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/asiapacific/death-toll-from-indonesia/1952654.html, title\u003dIndonesia military plane crash toll rises to 142, author\u003d(TEMPLATE)/rw/ec, pub\u003dChannel NewsAsia, date\u003dJuly 1, 2015]","TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://www.firstpost.com/world/at-least-116-feared-dead-in-indonesia-military-plane-crash-officials-2319964.html, title\u003dAt least 116 feared dead in Indonesia military plane crash: officials, author\u003d(TEMPLATE), pub\u003dfirstpost.com, date\u003dJune 30, 2015]"]],"links":[{"id":"Indonesia","description":"Indonesia"},{"id":"AirAsia","description":"AirAsia"},{"id":"Java_Sea","description":"Java Sea"}],"externalLinks":[],"sections":["Related news","Sister links","Sources"],"paragraphs":["TEMPLATE[date, July 4, 2015] TEMPLATE[aviation] On Tuesday, an TEMPLATE[w, Indonesian Air Force] TEMPLATE[w, C-130 Hercules] crashed in the city of TEMPLATE[w, Medan], Indonesia. All 122 people on board were killed as well as people on the ground in the city in TEMPLATE[w, North Sumatra], according to North Sumatra police Major A. Tarigan. Officials said the plane exploded on impact into a big fireball. TEMPLATE[image, [[w:sv:User:Erik l, Erik l]]] The military said the plane took off at 12:08 pm TEMPLATE[w, UTC+7, local time] (0508 TEMPLATE[w, UTC]) and crashed five TEMPLATE[w, kilometers] away a couple of minutes later. According to Agus Supriatna, chief of the Air Force, the pilot reported technical problems and requested return to base. The aircraft was en route from TEMPLATE[w, Soewondo Air Force Base] to TEMPLATE[w, Natuna].","The air force first said there were twelve crew members on board, but the total number of reported fatalities continued to change with later reports. Police found even more dead bodies from the crash on the ground, raising the reported death toll as high as 142 people. Some bodies have been identified by blood sampling, an official told newspaper TEMPLATE[w, Jakarta Globe].","There were some allegations that passengers on the aircraft were not limited to military families. The military is not allowed to fly civilian passengers, according to the air force chief, unless they are related to military personnel, or under some special circumstances. The chief is looking into these allegations to see if there were paying passengers.","An AirAsia jet crashed in the Java Sea last December, killing everyone aboard.","The cause of this C-130 crash has yet to be determined.","TEMPLATE[haveyoursay]","TEMPLATE[sisters, 2015 Indonesian Air Force Lockheed C-130 Hercules crash]","TEMPLATE[Publish] TEMPLATE[Archive]"],"categories":[{"id":"Category:Disasters_and_accidents","description":"Category:Disasters and accidents"},{"id":"Category:Aviation","description":"Category:Aviation"},{"id":"Category:Indonesia","description":"Category:Indonesia"},{"id":"Category:Asia","description":"Category:Asia"}],"templates":[{"name":"date","description":["July 4, 2015"]},{"name":"aviation","description":[]},{"name":"w","description":["Indonesian Air Force"]},{"name":"w","description":["C-130 Hercules"]},{"name":"w","description":["Medan"]},{"name":"w","description":["North Sumatra"]},{"name":"image","description":["[[w:sv:User:Erik l","Erik l]]"]},{"name":"w","description":["UTC+7","local time"]},{"name":"w","description":["UTC"]},{"name":"w","description":["kilometers"]},{"name":"w","description":["Soewondo Air Force Base"]},{"name":"w","description":["Natuna"]},{"name":"w","description":["Jakarta Globe"]},{"name":"haveyoursay","description":[]},{"name":"wikinews","description":["title\u003dAirAsia disaster: Bodies, wreckage found","date\u003dDecember 30, 2014"]},{"name":"wikinews","description":["title\u003dAirAsia jet vanishes over Indonesia, 162 missing","date\u003dDecember 28, 2014"]},{"name":"sisters","description":["2015 Indonesian Air Force Lockheed C-130 Hercules crash"]},{"name":"source","description":["url\u003dhttp://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-33339965","title\u003dIndonesia transport plane crash death toll rises","author\u003d","pub\u003dBBC News Online","date\u003dJuly 1, 2015"]},{"name":"source","description":["url\u003dhttp://www.military.com/daily-news/2015/07/01/indonesia-c130-crash-death-toll-at-141-as-search-effort-ends.html","title\u003dIndonesia C-130 Crash Death Toll at 141 as Search Effort Ends","author\u003dNiniek Karmini ([[Associated Press","AP]])","pub\u003dMilitary.com","date\u003dJuly 1, 2015"]},{"name":"source","description":["url\u003dhttp://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/asiapacific/death-toll-from-indonesia/1952654.html","title\u003dIndonesia military plane crash toll rises to 142","author\u003d(TEMPLATE)/rw/ec","pub\u003dChannel NewsAsia","date\u003dJuly 1, 2015"]},{"name":"source","description":["url\u003dhttp://www.firstpost.com/world/at-least-116-feared-dead-in-indonesia-military-plane-crash-officials-2319964.html","title\u003dAt least 116 feared dead in Indonesia military plane crash: officials","author\u003d(TEMPLATE)","pub\u003