{"title":"University defeat Toads in 2015 Sunshine Coast Rugby Union round 17","wikiTitle":"University_defeat_Toads_in_2015_Sunshine_Coast_Rugby_Union_round_17","wid":2324200,"lang":"en","namespace":"","integerNamespace":0,"timestamp":"2015-11-09T07:15:23Z","type":"ARTICLE","tables":[],"lists":[["TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttps://www.facebook.com/uscrugby/photos/a.703075323075847.1073741825.110718082311577/1000748776641832/?type\u003d1\u0026permPage\u003d1, title\u003dFull time in A Grade, author\u003dUSC Rugby, pub\u003dFacebook, date\u003dJuly 25, 2015]","TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttps://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid\u003d828089410639569\u0026id\u003d152478778200639, title\u003dA Grade, author\u003dSunshine Coast Rugby Union, pub\u003dFacebook, date\u003dJuly 25, 2015]"]],"links":[{"id":"Queensland","description":"Queensland"},{"id":"Sunshine_Coast_Rugby_Union","description":"Sunshine Coast Rugby Union"},{"id":"University_of_the_Sunshine_Coast_Rugby_Union_Club","description":"University"},{"id":"Toads_Rugby_Union_Club","description":"Toads"},{"id":"Australia","description":"Australia"}],"externalLinks":[],"sections":["Sources"],"paragraphs":["TEMPLATE[date, July 25, 2015] TEMPLATE[Footballbox-ver, date\u003d July 25, 2015\u003cbr\u003e16:00 (UTC+10), team1\u003d Toads, score1\u003d 17, team2\u003d University, score2 \u003d 45, report\u003d, goals1\u003d, goals2\u003d, stadium\u003d Victory Park, Woombye\u003cbr\u003eAustralia, attendance\u003d, right] TEMPLATE[image, media\u003dvideo, Patrick Gillett] In Queensland\u0027s Sunshine Coast Rugby Union, University defeated Toads 45 points to 17 at TEMPLATE[w, Woombye, Queensland, Woombye], Australia this afternoon. They opened the scoring after 18 minutes with an TEMPLATE[w, Laws of Rugby Union, anchor\u003dTries and conversions, unconverted try].","Toads scored their first points three minutes later but would not score again until the nine minute mark of the second half. By this point University had scored three more tries \u0026mdash; two of which were converted \u0026mdash; and two penalty goals.","University ran in two tries to one after this to wrap up the 28 point win. TEMPLATE[w, Caloundra Rugby Union Club, Caloundra] defeated TEMPLATE[w, Maroochydore Rugby Union Club, Maroochydore] by 7 points in the other A Grade game.","TEMPLATE[haveyoursay]","TEMPLATE[Original]","TEMPLATE[Publish] TEMPLATE[Archive]"],"categories":[{"id":"Category:Australia","description":"Category:Australia"},{"id":"Category:Rugby","description":"Category:Rugby"},{"id":"Category:Oceania","description":"Category:Oceania"},{"id":"Category:Sports","description":"Category:Sports"},{"id":"Category:University_of_the_Sunshine_Coast_Rugby_Union_Club","description":"Category:University of the Sunshine Coast Rugby Union Club"},{"id":"Category:Toads_Rugby_Union_Club","description":"Category:Toads Rugby Union Club"},{"id":"Category:Queensland","description":"Category:Queensland"},{"id":"Category:Sunshine_Coast_Rugby_Union","description":"Category:Sunshine Coast Rugby Union"},{"id":"Category:RockerballAustralia_(Wikinewsie)","description":"Category:RockerballAustralia (Wikinewsie)"}],"templates":[{"name":"date","description":["July 25, 2015"]},{"name":"Footballbox-ver","description":["date\u003d July 25, 2015\u003cbr\u003e16:00 (UTC+10)","team1\u003d Toads","score1\u003d 17","team2\u003d University","score2 \u003d 45","report\u003d","goals1\u003d","goals2\u003d","stadium\u003d Victory Park, Woombye\u003cbr\u003eAustralia","attendance\u003d","right"]},{"name":"image","description":["media\u003dvideo","Patrick Gillett"]},{"name":"w","description":["Woombye, Queensland","Woombye"]},{"name":"w","description":["Laws of Rugby Union","anchor\u003dTries and conversions","unconverted try"]},{"name":"w","description":["Caloundra Rugby Union Club","Caloundra"]},{"name":"w","description":["Maroochydore Rugby Union Club","Maroochydore"]},{"name":"haveyoursay","description":[]},{"name":"Original","description":[]},