{"title":"Former Indian president APJ Abdul Kalam dies at age 83","wikiTitle":"Former_Indian_president_APJ_Abdul_Kalam_dies_at_age_83","wid":2328072,"lang":"en","namespace":"","integerNamespace":0,"timestamp":"2015-10-14T15:48:07Z","type":"ARTICLE","tables":[],"lists":[["TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://www.hindustantimes.com/india-news/former-president-abdul-kalam-hospitalised-in-shillong-after-collapsing-during-speech/article1-1373696.aspx, title\u003d\u0027Missile Man\u0027: Ex-president APJ Abdul Kalam passes away, author\u003dRahul Karmakar and Rezaul H Laskar, pub\u003dHindustan Times, date\u003dJuly 28, 2015]","TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://www.firstpost.com/india/former-president-apj-abdul-kalam-passes-away-after-collapsing-during-lecture-at-iim-shillong-2366030.html, title\u003dEnd of an era: \u0027Missile man\u0027 APJ Abdul Kalam passes away after cardiac arrest in Shillong, author\u003d, pub\u003dFirstpost, date\u003dJuly 28, 2015]"]],"links":[],"externalLinks":[],"sections":["Sources"],"paragraphs":["TEMPLATE[correction, date\u003dOctober 14, 2015, explanation\u003dThe UTC conversion here is incorrect \u0026mdash; 6:30pm IST is 1300 UTC, not 0000UTC the next day.] TEMPLATE[date, July 28, 2015] TEMPLATE[India] TEMPLATE[image, M. Prasanna Kumar] Yesterday, former Indian president TEMPLATE[w, APJ Abdul Kalam] died at the age of 83 after collapsing at about 6:30 p.m. TEMPLATE[w, Indian Standard Time, local time] (0000 today TEMPLATE[w, UTC]) while delivering a speech about Livable Planet Earth at the TEMPLATE[w, Indian Institute of Management Shillong], in TEMPLATE[w, Meghalaya], TEMPLATE[w, India]. Abdul Kalam was taken to Bethany Hospital\u0027s TEMPLATE[wikt, intensive care unit] and was declared dead about an hour and a half later.","Some army doctors were sent from TEMPLATE[w, North Eastern Indira Gandhi Regional Institute of Health and Medical Sciences]. According to doctors at Bethany Hospital, Kalam was dead by 7 p.m. but they waited for the arrival of Meghalaya chief minister TEMPLATE[w, V. Shanmuganathan], about an hour later, before announcing the death.","TEMPLATE[w, LC Goyal], home secretary, said the Indian government will declare a seven day national mourning for Kalam. Home minister TEMPLATE[w, Rajnath Singh] TEMPLATE[w, twitter, tweeted], \"He was an inspiration to an entire generation.\"","Kalam\u0027s presidential term completed in July 2007. TEMPLATE[haveyoursay]","TEMPLATE[Publish] TEMPLATE[Archive]"],"categories":[{"id":"Category:India","description":"Category:India"},{"id":"Category:Asia","description":"Category:Asia"},{"id":"Category:Politics_and_conflicts","description":"Category:Politics and conflicts"}],"templates":[{"name":"correction","description":["date\u003dOctober 14, 2015","explanation\u003dThe UTC conversion here is incorrect \u0026mdash; 6:30pm IST is 1300 UTC, not 0000UTC the next day."]},{"name":"date","description":["July 28, 2015"]},{"name":"India","description":[]},{"name":"image","description":["M. Prasanna Kumar"]},{"name":"w","description":["APJ Abdul Kalam"]},{"name":"w","description":["Indian Standard Time","local time"]},{"name":"w","description":["UTC"]},{"name":"w","description":["Indian Institute of Management Shillong"]},{"name":"w","description":["Meghalaya"]},{"name":"w","description":["India"]},{"name":"wikt","description":["intensive care unit"]},{"name":"w","description":["North Eastern Indira Gandhi Regional Institute of Health and Medical Sciences"]},{"name":"w","description":["V. Shanmuganathan"]},{"name":"w","description":["LC Goyal"]},{"name":"w","description":["Rajnath Singh"]},{"name":"w","description":["twitter","tweeted"]},{"name":"haveyoursay","description":[]},{"name":"source","description":["url\u003dhttp://www.hindustantimes.com/india-news/former-president-abdul-kalam-hospitalised-in-shillong-after-collapsing-during-speech/article1-1373696.aspx","title\u003d\u0027Missile Man\u0027: Ex-president APJ Abdul Kalam passes away","author\u003dRahul Karmakar and Rezaul H Laskar","pub\u003dHindustan Times","date\u003dJuly 28, 2015"]},{"name":"source","description":["url\u003dhttp://www.firstpost.com/india/former-president-apj-abdul-kalam-passes-away-after-collapsing-during-lecture-at-iim-shillong-2366030.html","title\u003dEnd of an era: \u0027Missile man\u0027 APJ Abdul Kalam passes away after cardiac arrest in Shillong","author\u003d","pub\u003dFirstpost","date\u003dJuly 28, 2015"]},{"name":"Publish","description":[]},{"name":"Archive","description":[]}],"templatesSchema":["date","explanation","url","title","author","pub","date","url","title","author","pub","date"],"highlights":["Livable Planet Earth"]}
{"title":"Local municipalities in Italy ask taxes from religious schools","wikiTitle":"Local_municipalities_in_Italy_ask_taxes_from_religious_schools","wid":2334812,"lang":"en","namespace":"","integerNamespace":0,"timestamp":"2015-08-13T13:08:54Z","type":"ARTICLE","tables":[],"lists":[["TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://www.uaar.it/uaar/campagne/ici-private, title\u003dIci/Imu/Tasi per le scuole private paritarie!, author\u003d, pub\u003dUAAR, pubtarget\u003dUnion of Rationalist Atheists and Agnostics, date\u003dAugust 2, 2015 (date of access), lang\u003dItalian]"],["TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://www.ilfattoquotidiano.it/2015/07/30/imu-bogliasco-guerra-sindaco-prete-asilo-e-casa-riposo-paghino-no-esentati/1922216/, title\u003dImu, Bogliasco: guerra sindaco-prete. âAsilo e casa riposo paghinoâ. âNo, esentatiâ, author\u003dRenzo Parodi, pub\u003dIl Fatto Quotidiano, date\u003dJuly 30, 2015, lang\u003dItalian]"],["TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://laprovinciadisondrio.it/stories/Cronaca/ici-alle-scuole-paritarie-colpite-le-materne_1133498_11/, title\u003dIci alle scuole paritarie, colpite le materne, author\u003d, pub\u003dLa Provincia di Sondrio, pubtarget\u003dit:La Provincia di Sondrio, date\u003dJuly 30, 2015, lang\u003dItalian]"],["TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://www.infodata.ilsole24ore.com/2015/07/30/scuole-e-imu-nessun-cambiamento-per-le-13-625-scuole-paritarie-italiane/?refresh_ce\u003d1, title\u003dScuole e Imu, nessun cambiamento per le 13.625 scuole paritarie italiane, author\u003dInfodata, pub\u003dIl Sole 24 Ore, date\u003dJuly 30, 2015, lang\u003dItalian]"],["TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://www.avvenire.it/Cronaca/Pagine/Paritarie-le-norme-dimenticate-.aspx, title\u003dScuole paritarie e tasse, le norme dimenticate, author\u003dEnrico Lenzi, pub\u003dAvvenire, date\u003dJuly 29, 2015, lang\u003dItalian]"],["TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://www.milanotoday.it/politica/scuole-private-lombarde-ici-m5s-lombardia-sessione-bilancio.html, title\u003dLe scuole private lombarde devono pagare l\u0027Ici: ordine del giorno del M5s Lombardia per la sessione di bilancio, author\u003d, pub\u003dMilano Today, date\u003dJuly 28, 2015, lang\u003dItalian]"],["TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://temi.repubblica.it/micromega-online/ici-e-chiesa-lo-scandalo-della-%E2%80%9Clegge-uguale-per-tutti%E2%80%9D/, title\u003dICI e Chiesa, lo scandalo della âlegge uguale per tuttiâ, author\u003dTobia Invernizzi, pub\u003dMicroMega, date\u003dJuly 28, 2015, lang\u003dItalian]"],["TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://www.repubblica.it/politica/2015/07/26/news/ici_i_vescovi_protestano_il_governo_le_paritarie_non_pagheranno_-119841351/, title\u003dIci, i vescovi protestano. Il governo: \"Le paritarie non pagheranno\", author\u003d, pub\u003dla Repubblica, date\u003dJuly 26, 2015, lang\u003dItalian]"],["TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://www.repubblica.it/scuola/2015/07/25/news/scuola_la_cei_insorge_sentenza_su_paritarie_pericolosa_limita_la_liberta_-119788721/, title\u003dScuola, la Cei insorge: \"Sentenza su Ici a paritarie pericolosa\". Giannini non si sbilancia: \"C\u0027Ã¨ una riflessione da fare\", author\u003d, pub\u003dla Repubblica, date\u003dJuly 25, 2015, lang\u003dItalian]"],["TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://milano.repubblica.it/cronaca/2015/07/25/news/scuole_religiose_reione_ombardia_pronti_a_sostenere_le_scuole-119804567/?ref\u003dHREA-1, title\u003dScuole cattoliche e tasse sugli immobili, Maroni studia misure ad hoc per sostenere gli istituti, author\u003d, pub\u003dla Repubblica, date\u003dJuly 25, 2015, lang\u003dItalian]"],["TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://www.ilfattoquotidiano.it/2015/07/24/ici-imu-alla-chiesa-la-cassazione-ha-ragione-il-comune-di-livorno-le-scuole-religiose-devono-pagarla/1903904/, title\u003dIci-Imu alla Chiesa, la Cassazione: âHa ragione il Comune di Livorno, le scuole religiose devono pagarlaâ, author\u003dFQ(TEMPLATE), pub\u003dIl Fatto Quotidiano, date\u003dJuly 24, 2015, lang\u003dItalian]"],["TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://firenze.repubblica.it/cronaca/2015/07/24/news/livorno_sentenza_cassazione_le_scuole_religiose_devono_pagare_la_tassa_sugli_immobili_-119743949/, title\u003dLivorno, sentenza Cassazione: \"Le scuole religiose devono pagare la tassa sugli immobili\", author\u003d, pub\u003dla Repubblica, date\u003dJuly 24, 2015, lang\u003dItalian]"]],"links":[],"externalLinks":[],"sections":["Sources"],"paragraphs":["TEMPLATE[date, August 2, 2015] TEMPLATE[Italy] In the past few days in TEMPLATE[w, Italy], several municipalities have started asking religious schools to pay taxes for property and local services, despite the resistance of the TEMPLATE[w, Roman Catholicism, Catholic Church].","The request of the municipalities results from the sentence of the Italian TEMPLATE[w, Supreme Court of Cassation (Italy), Supreme Court of Cassation] on July 8, recognising as legitimate the request of the Municipality of TEMPLATE[w, Livorno] asking religious schools to pay property taxes.","Requests have come from the Municipality of TEMPLATE[w, Bogliasco], next to TEMPLATE[w, Genova], and from the deputies of TEMPLATE[w, Five Star Movement, Movimento 5 Stelle] (M5S) of the regional counsel of TEMPLATE[w, Lombardy]. The first case is of the mayor Luca Pastorino that in last years received several refusals of his requests for payment because of the religious nursery school and retirement home. In the second case, the M5S party asks to the regional government to assure the local administrations of the region regularly apply the sentence of the Supreme Court.","The case on which the Court has ruled was of the religious schools Santo Spirito and Immacolata in Livorno, TEMPLATE[w, Tuscany], to pay over 422,000 TEMPLATE[w, euro, euros] in arrears for the period from 2004 to 2009. The request was advanced by the Municipality of Livorno in 2010.","The city reasoned, TEMPLATE[translated_quote, it, Italian language, poichÃ© gli utenti della scuola paritaria pagano un corrispettivo per la frequenza, tale attivitÃ  Ã¨ di carattere commerciale, because the users of the private schools pay a frequency fee, this kind of activity is considered as a commercial one].","In 2014 the Italian municipal tax discipline has changed from the ICI system to the IMU system by the TEMPLATE[w, Mario Monti, Monti] government. A mean cost per student criterion is used to tax only the schools that receive a fee higher than the mean cost per student fixed by the State.  The new law is not retroactive, so the taxes requested in arrears from 2006 to 2009 are under the ICI system.","Minister of Education TEMPLATE[w, Stefania Giannini] said a TEMPLATE[translated_quote, it, Italian language, riflessione piÃ¹ generale, more general reflection] is needed.  Claudio De Vincenti, undersecretary to the prime minister, said TEMPLATE[translated_quote, it, Italian language, apriremo quindi un tavolo di confronto con le organizzazioni non profit, comprese quelle religiose, a discussion table will be opened with the non-profit associations, religious association included].","Undersecretary for Education Mr. Toccafondi says TEMPLATE[translated_quote, it, Italian language, Molti istituti aumenteranno le rette o chiuderanno. CosÃ¬ lo Stato dovrÃ  trovare nuove risorse per costruire nuove strutture e gestirle, many schools will increase their fees or they will quit. Then the State will have to find new resources to build new structures and manage them].","Also the president of the Lombardy region, TEMPLATE[w, Roberto Maroni], has reacted by proposing some regional counter-measures to finance private schools.","The secretary general of CEI (TEMPLATE[w, Italian Episcopal Conference]), TEMPLATE[w, Nunzio Galantino], has called the sentence TEMPLATE[translated_quote, it, Italian language, pericolosa, dangerous] and TEMPLATE[translated_quote, it, Italian language, \"ideologica, ideological]: TEMPLATE[translated_quote, it, Italian language, Siamo davanti a una sentenza pericolosa. Chi prende decisioni, lo faccia con meno ideologia. PerchÃ© ho la netta sensazione che con questo modo di pensare, si aspetti l\u0027applauso di qualche parte ideologizzata. Il fatto Ã¨ che non ci si sta rendendo conto del servizio che svolgono le scuole pubbliche paritarie, We face a dangerous sentence. Who takes the decisions, do it with less ideology. Because I have the clear sensation that with this way of thinking, they wait the praise of some \u0027\u0027ideologized\u0027\u0027 supporters. Indeed, they don\u0027t understand what kind of good service private schools held].","Italian secularist associations are concerned the Government will modify the law in order to maintain an exception for religious schools. The secularist magazine TEMPLATE[w, MicroMega] describe the court\u0027s judgement as historic.","The TEMPLATE[w, Union of Rationalist Atheists and Agnostics] (UAAR) has launched a petition which now has more than 11,000 signatures, asking the government to respect and execute the sentence of the Supreme Court. It is also encouraging citizens to ask for application of the law in their local municipalities.","TEMPLATE[haveyoursay]","TEMPLATE[Publish] TEMPLATE[Archive]"],"categories":[{"id":"Category:_Education","description":"Category: Education"},{"id":"Category:Italy","description":"Category:Italy"},{"id":"Category:Roman_Catholic_Church","description":"Category:Roman Catholic Church"},{"id":"Category:Europe","description":"Category:Europe"},{"id":"Category:European_Union","description":"Category:European Union"},{"id":"Category:Christianity","description":"Category:Christianity"},{"id":"Category:Religion","description":"Category:Religion"},{"id":"Category:Politics_and_conflicts","description":"Category:Politics and conflicts"}],"templates":[{"name":"date","description":["August 2, 2015"]},{"name":"Italy","description":[]},{"name":"w","description":["Italy"]},{"name":"w","description":["Roman Catholicism","Catholic Church"]},{"name":"w","description":["Supreme Court of Cassation (Italy)","Supreme Court of Cassation"]},{"name":"w","description":["Livorno"]},{"name":"w","description":["Bogliasco"]},{"name":"w","description":["Genova"]},{"name":"w","description":["Five Star Movement","Movimento 5 Stelle"]},{"name":"w","description":["Lombardy"]},{"name":"w","description":["Tuscany"]},{"name":"w","description":["euro","euros"]},{"name":"translated_quote","description":["it","Italian language","poichÃ© gli utenti della scuola paritaria pagano un corrispettivo per la frequenza, tale attivitÃ  Ã¨ di carattere commerciale","because the users of the private schools pay a frequency fee, this kind of activity is considered as a commercial one"]},{"name":"w","description":["Mario Monti","Monti"]},{"name":"w","description":["Stefania Giannini"]},{"name":"translated_quote","description":["it","Italian language","riflessione piÃ¹ generale","more general reflection"]},{"name":"translated_quote","description":["it","Italian language","apriremo quindi un tavolo di confronto con le organizzazioni non profit, comprese quelle religiose","a discussion table will be opened with the non-profit associations, religious association included"]},{"name":"translated_quote","description":["it","Italian language","Molti istituti aumenteranno le rette o chiuderanno. CosÃ¬ lo Stato dovrÃ  trovare nuove risorse per costruire nuove strutture e gestirle","many schools will increase their fees or they will quit. Then the State will have to find new resources to build new structures and manage them"]},{"name":"w","description":["Roberto Maroni"]},{"name":"w","description":["Italian Episcopal Conference"]},{"name":"w","description":["Nunzio Galantino"]},{"name":"translated_quote","description":["it","Italian language","pericolosa","dangerous"]},{"name":"translated_quote","description":["it","Italian language","\"ideologica","ideological"]},{"name":"translated_quote","description":["it","Italian language","Siamo davanti a una sentenza pericolosa. Chi prende de