 (TEMPLATE)","time\u003d15:00 CET","team1\u003d[[Arsenal F.C.","Arsenal]]","score\u003d1â0","team2\u003d[[Chelsea F.C.","Chelsea]]","goals1\u003d(TEMPLATE) (TEMPLATE)","goals2\u003d","stadium\u003d(TEMPLATE), [[London]]","attendance\u003d 85,437","referee\u003d(TEMPLATE) ((TEMPLATE))"]},{"name":"w","description":["British Summer Time","BST"]},{"name":"w","description":["Alex Oxlade-Chamberlain","Oxlade-Chamberlain"]},{"name":"goal","description":["24"]},{"name":"w","description":["Wembley Stadium"]},{"name":"w","description":["Anthony Taylor (referee)","Anthony Taylor"]},{"name":"w","description":["Cheshire County Football Association","Cheshire"]},{"name":"source","description":["url\u003dhttp://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-3182844/Arsenal-vs-Chelsea-FA-Community-Shield-2015-LIVE-football-score-London-rivals-kick-new-season-Wembley.html","title\u003dArsenal 1-0 Chelsea Community Shield 2015 RESULT: Alex Oxlade-Chamberlain beats champions with fine goal at Wembley","author\u003dJonny Singer","pub\u003dDaily Mail","date\u003dAugust 3, 2015"]},{"name":"source","description":["url\u003dhttp://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/33667216","title\u003dArsenal 1-0 Chelsea","author\u003dAndy Cryer","pub\u003dBBC Sport","date\u003dAugust 2, 2015"]},{"name":"source","description":["url\u003dhttp://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/teams/arsenal/11769945/Arsenal-1-0-Chelsea-Community-Shield-2015-as-it-happened.html","title\u003dArsenal 1-0 Chelsea, Community Shield 2015: as it happened","author\u003dAdam Hurrey","pub\u003dThe Sunday Telegraph","date\u003dAugust 2, 2015"]},{"name":"source","description":["url\u003dhttp://www.thefa.com/news/competitions/fa-community-shield/2015/aug/chelsea-v-arsenal-fa-community-shield-match-report","title\u003dArsenal brush aside Chelsea to lift Community Shield","author\u003dJamie Reid","pub\u003dThe FA","date\u003dAugust 2, 2015"]},{"name":"Publish","description":[]},{"name":"Archive","description":[]}],"templatesSchema":["date","t