{"title":"FC Barcelona defeats AS Roma 3-0 to win 2015 Joan Gamper Trophy","wikiTitle":"FC_Barcelona_defeats_AS_Roma_3-0_to_win_2015_Joan_Gamper_Trophy","wid":2347955,"lang":"en","namespace":"","integerNamespace":0,"timestamp":"2016-06-19T00:47:21Z","type":"ARTICLE","tables":[],"lists":[["TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://www.fcbarcelona.com/football/first-team/match-archive/2015-2016/joan-gamper-trophy/fc-barcelona_roma/info, title\u003dFC Barcelona - Roma, 08/05/2015 (TEMPLATE) FC Barcelona, author\u003d, pub\u003dFC Barcelona, date\u003dAugust 7, 2015 (date of access)]","TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://www.fcbarcelona.com/football/first-team/match-archive/2015-2016/joan-gamper-trophy/fc-barcelona_roma/minute-by-minute-fcb-roma, title\u003dFC Barcelona - Roma, 08/05/2015 (TEMPLATE) FC Barcelona, author\u003d, pub\u003dFC Barcelona, date\u003dAugust 7, 2015 (date of access)]","TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://www.theguardian.com/football/2015/aug/06/barcelona-roma-lionel-messi-neymar, title\u003dBarcelona\u0027s Lionel Messi appears to head-butt Roma defender in friendly, author\u003d(TEMPLATE), pub\u003dThe Guardian, date\u003dAugust 6, 2015]","TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/players/lionel-messi/11786620/Lionel-Messi-headbutts-Roma-defender-during-bad-tempered-friendly-clash.html, title\u003dLionel Messi \u0027headbutts\u0027 Roma defender during bad-tempered friendly clash, author\u003d, pub\u003dThe Daily Telegraph, date\u003dAugust 6, 2015]","TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://www.gazzetta.it/Calcio/Serie-A/Roma/05-08-2015/barcellona-roma-3-0-decidono-messi-neymar-rakitic-120838414829.shtml?refresh_ce-cp, author\u003d, title\u003dBarcellona-Roma 3-0: decidono Messi, Neymar e Rakitic, pub\u003dLa Gazzetta dello Sport, date\u003dAugust 6, 2015, lang\u003dItalian]","TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://www.sbnation.com/soccer/2015/8/5/9103825/lionel-messi-attacks-yanga-mbiwa-headbutt-throat-grab-barcelona-roma, title\u003dLionel Messi loses his mind, head butts, grabs Roma playerâs throat, author\u003dConor Dowley, pub\u003dSB Nation, date\u003dAugust 5, 2015]"]],"links":[{"id":"FC_Barcelona","description":"FC Barcelona"}],"externalLinks":[],"sections":["Sources"],"paragraphs":["TEMPLATE[date, August 7, 2015] TEMPLATE[football] TEMPLATE[image, [[c:User:Gabrielcorbachobermejo, Gabrielcorbachobermejo]]] On Wednesday, TEMPLATE[w, Catalonia]-based football club FC Barcelona defeated TEMPLATE[w, Rome]-based TEMPLATE[w, Italy, Italian] TEMPLATE[w, Serie A] football club TEMPLATE[w, A.S. Roma] 3\u0026ndash;0 in the 2015 TEMPLATE[w, Joan Gamper Trophy] played in TEMPLATE[w, Camp Nou] stadium, TEMPLATE[w, Barcelona].","Barcelona had stronger possession of the ball in front of Roma. The match saw only five TEMPLATE[w, yellow card (association football), yellow cards], two for Barcelona players and three for AS Roma players. A total of twenty fouls were committed in the match. TEMPLATE[w, Brazil, Brazilian] TEMPLATE[w, Neymar] scored the first goal of the match in the 26th minute, TEMPLATE[w, assist (football), assisted] by TEMPLATE[w, JÃ©rÃ©my Mathieu]. Messi doubled the lead by scoring in the bottom right corner in the 41st minute, assisted by Neymar. The first half ended in 2\u0026ndash;0 with four bookings.","TEMPLATE[w, Ivan RakitiÄ] scored the last goal of the match in the 66th minute. The TEMPLATE[w, Croatia, Croat] scored a right-footed 30-TEMPLATE[w, yard] TEMPLATE[wikt, screamer] in the top corner, assisted by TEMPLATE[w, Sergio Busquets]. After the match, Rakitic said: \"The aim is to keep on the same lines as we were at the end of last season [...] I feel strong and the team is working well. This was only a friendly but we still played to win as in any match.\"","Barcelona\u0027s new signings TEMPLATE[w, Aleix Vidal] and TEMPLATE[w, Adra Turan] could not play the match due to a transfer ban.","BarÃ§a is to face TEMPLATE[w, Athletic Bilbao] on August 23 in TEMPLATE[w, 2015â16 La Liga, 2015/16] TEMPLATE[w, La Liga].","In the 34th minute, TEMPLATE[w, Marc Bartra]\u0027s pass to Messi was called TEMPLATE[w, Offside (association football), offside]. Moments later, Messi and Roma\u0027s TEMPLATE[w, Mapou Yanga-Mbiwa] confronted each other, culminating with Messi TEMPLATE[w, Headbutt, headbutting] Yanga-Mbiwa and grabbing him by the throat. Messi did not receive a TEMPLATE[w, red card (association football), red card], although both players were booked. The referee came to stop the dispute.","TEMPLATE[haveyoursay]TEMPLATE[clear]","TEMPLATE[footballbox, date       \u003d 5 August 2015, team1      \u003d (TEMPLATE), score      \u003d 3â0, team2      \u003d (TEMPLATE), goals1     \u003d (TEMPLATE) (TEMPLATE)\u003cbr\u003e(TEMPLATE) (TEMPLATE), (TEMPLATE)\u003cbr\u003e(TEMPLATE) (TEMPLATE)\u003cbr\u003e(TEMPLATE) (TEMPLATE), goals2     \u003d (TEMPLATE) (TEMPLATE)\u003cbr\u003e(TEMPLATE) (TEMPLATE)\u003cbr\u003e(TEMPLATE) (TEMPLATE), stadium    \u003d (TEMPLATE), location   \u003d (TEMPLATE), (TEMPLATE), attendance \u003d 94,422, referee    \u003d (TEMPLATE) ((TEMPLATE)), result     \u003d W]","TEMPLATE[Publish] TEMPLATE[Archive]"],"categories":[{"id":"Category:Football_(soccer)","description":"Category:Football (soccer)"},{"id":"Category:Football_Match_Reports","description":"Category:Football Match Reports"},{"id":"Category:Barcelona","description":"Category:Barcelona"},{"id":"Category:FC_Barcelona","description":"Category:FC Barcelona"},{"id":"Category:Spain","description":"Category:Spain"},{"id":"Category:Europe","description":"Category:Europe"},{"id":"Category:Rome","description":"Category:Rome"},{"id":"Category:Italy","description":"Category:Italy"},{"id":"Category:La_Liga","description":"Category:La Liga"},{"id":"Category:AS_Roma","description":"Category:AS Roma"},{"id":"Category:Sports","description":"Category:Sports"},{"id":"Category:Ivan_RakitiÄ","description":"Category:Ivan RakitiÄ"}],"templates":[{"name":"date","description":["August 7, 2015"]}