{"title":"Malaysia to investigate suspected plane debris washed ashore on several Maldives islands","wikiTitle":"Malaysia_to_investigate_suspected_plane_debris_washed_ashore_on_several_Maldives_islands","wid":2356121,"lang":"en","namespace":"","integerNamespace":0,"timestamp":"2015-09-26T16:12:12Z","type":"ARTICLE","tables":[],"lists":[["TEMPLATE[wikinews, title\u003dSuspected plane debris washes ashore on several Maldives islands, date\u003dAugust 9, 2015]"],["TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://www.scmp.com/news/china/society/article/1848329/no-absolute-certainty-yet-reunion-island-wing-piece-part-missing, title\u003d\u0027No absolute certainty yet\u0027 Reunion Island wing piece part of missing flight MH370, author\u003dLaura Zhou, pub\u003dSouth China Morning Post, date\u003dAugust 10, 2015]","TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://news.sky.com/story/1533314/mh370-debris-search-spreads-to-maldives, title\u003dMH370 Debris Search Spreads To Maldives, author\u003d, pub\u003dSky News, date\u003dAugust 10, 2015]","TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-33846493, title\u003dMH370: Malaysia sends experts to examine Maldives \u0027debris\u0027, author\u003d, pub\u003dBBC News Online, date\u003dAugust 10, 2015]","TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://news.yahoo.com/malaysia-verify-debris-maldives-came-plane-105657770.html, title\u003dMalaysia to verify if debris in Maldives came from plane, author\u003d(TEMPLATE), pub\u003dYahoo! News, date\u003dAugust 10, 2015]","TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://www.reuters.com/article/2015/08/10/us-malaysia-airlines-crash-idUSKCN0QF0YF20150810, title\u003dMalaysia to inspect suspected plane debris found in Maldives, author\u003dAl-Zaquan Amer Hamzah and Praveen Menon, pub\u003dReuters, date\u003dAugust 10, 2015]"]],"links":[],"externalLinks":[],"sections":["Related news","Sources"],"paragraphs":["TEMPLATE[date, August 10, 2015] TEMPLATE[Aviation] After published reports stated suspected plane debris washed up on several TEMPLATE[w, Maldives] islands, TEMPLATE[w, Malaysia] has stated it will send a team of investigators to examine it. Investigators are to try to determine if the debris came from a plane before taking any further action.","\"I urge all parties to allow for the verification process to take its due course. Once it is determined to be aircraft debris, discussions will be held to determine next steps in terms of the process of analysis. Undue speculation will only stress the families and loved ones, anxiously awaiting news on this matter,\" said TEMPLATE[w, Liow Tiong Lai], Malaysia\u0027s Transport Minister in a statement.","An investigation into the debris was launched after an photos of the debris were uploaded to the social networking TEMPLATE[w, website] TEMPLATE[w, Facebook] on, reportedly, May 31, by an employee of a beach resort. Some of the debris is reported to have washed ashore as early as May 31 and was found on a beach owned by the Banyan Tree Vabbinfaru resort, located in TEMPLATE[w, Kaafu Atoll]. In the past few days, several other pieces of debris were recovered on at least three other islands. Authorities are trying to determine if it may be part of TEMPLATE[w, Malaysia Airlines Flight 370] (MH370).","Last week, a piece of a wing known as a TEMPLATE[w, flaperon] was found washed ashore on TEMPLATE[w, RÃ©union] Island. The Malaysian government stated it\u0027s from MH370, but according to TEMPLATE[w, China, Chinese] officials, the piece has yet to be confirmed to be from MH370 because managers were on leave from the TEMPLATE[w, Spain, Spanish] manufacturer of the part.","However, before most of the debris could be examined, it had already been taken away for disposal. The photographs showed a large white object, possibly two, stained with TEMPLATE[w, algae] and appear to be made of a TEMPLATE[w, fiberglass] and honeycomb material. The objects appear to be several TEMPLATE[w, foot (unit), feet] in length and width and in one photo where the paint is severely peeled, red letters \"IC\" can be seen.  Those pieces, along with others, were taken away and disposed of as trash. When authorities discovered the photographs, they returned to the site, but only found a small, five to seven TEMPLATE[w, inch] (about 13\u0026ndash;18\u0026nbsp;TEMPLATE[w, centimetre, cm]) piece of debris they say doesn\u0027t appear to be part of a plane.","Some of the debris may not be from a plane. Abdulla Rasheed, a captain of a cargo boat which recently capsized in the waters off the Maldives, stated, \"From the pictures of the debris found on most of the islands, I can almost certainly say that they are from the cargo we were carrying\". Despite this possibility, any debris located is being gathered up and stored in a warehouse until Malaysian authorities can examine it.","\"We are collecting any unidentified debris and storing them in a warehouse so that the Malaysians can carry out tests and determine if it is from their plane or not,\" said the office of the Maldives President in a statement reported by TEMPLATE[w, Haveeru Daily].","MH370, while flying from TEMPLATE[w, Kuala Lumpur], Malaysia to TEMPLATE[w, Beijing], China, vanished without a trace on March 8, 2014. All 239 passengers and crew are believed to be dead. On the day the plane went missing, residents on the small Maldive island of TEMPLATE[w, Kudahuvadhoo] claimed to have seen a very \"low flying jumbo jet\" crash into the Indian Ocean. Some also noted the colors appeared to resemble that of a TEMPLATE[w, Malaysia Airlines] plane. \"Iâve never seen a jet flying so low over our island before. We\u0027ve seen seaplanes, but I\u0027m sure that this was not one of those. I could even make out the doors on the plane clearly\", one resident was quoted as saying to the newspaper Haveeru Daily. Some claim the plane appeared to he headed in the direction of TEMPLATE[w, Diego Garcia], but Malaysian authorities have discounted those claims.","\"Based on the monitoring up to date, no indication of Flight MH370 has been observed on any military radars in the country [Maldives]. Furthermore, the data of radars at Maldives airports have also been analysed and shows no indication of the said flight,\" said Malaysia\u0027s transport ministry at the time of the report.","TEMPLATE[haveyoursay]","TEMPLATE[Publish] TEMPLATE[Archive]"],"categories":[{"id":"Category:Malaysia","description":"Category:Malaysia"},{"id":"Category:Maldives","description":"Category:Maldives"},{"id":"Category:Disasters_and_accidents","description":"Category:Disasters and accidents"},{"id":"Category:Aviation","description":"Category:Aviation"},{"id":"Category:RÃ©union","description":"Category:RÃ©union"},{"id":"Category:France","description":"Category:France"},{"id":"Category:Asia","description":"Category:Asia"},{"id":"Category:Europe","description":"Category:Europe"},{"id":"Category:Malaysia_Airlines","description":"Category:Malaysia Airlines"},{"id":"Category:Malaysia_Airlines_Flight_370","description":"Category:Malaysia Airlines Flight 370"},{"id":"Category:British_Indian_Ocean_Territory","description":"Category:British Indian Ocean Territory"}],"templates":[{"name":"date","description":["August 10, 2015"]},{"name":"Aviation","description":[]},{"name":"w","description":["Maldives"]},{"name":"w","description":["Malaysia"]},{"name":"w","description":["Liow Tiong Lai"]},{"name":"w","description":["website"]},{"name":"w","description":["Facebook"]},{"name":"w","description":["Kaafu Atoll"]},{"name":"w","description":["Malaysia Airlines Flight 370"]},{"name":"w","description":["flaperon"]},{"name":"w","description":["RÃ©union"]},{"name":"w","description":["China","Chinese"]},{"name":"w","description":["Spain","Spanish"]},{"name":"w","description":["algae"]},{"name":"w","description":["fiberglass"]},{"name":"w","description":["foot (unit)","feet"]},{"name":"w","description":["inch"]},{"name":"w","description":["centimetre","cm"]},{"name":"w","description":["Haveeru Daily"]},{"name":"w","description":["Kuala Lumpur"]},{"name":"w","description":["Beijing"]},{"name":"w","description":["Kudahuvadhoo"]},{"name":"w","description":["Malaysia Airlines"]},{"name":"w","description":["Diego Garcia"]},{"name":"haveyoursay","description":[]},{"name":"wikinews","description":["title\u003dSuspected plane debris washes ashore on several Maldives islands","date\u003dAugust 9, 2015"]},{"name":"source","description":["url\u003dhttp://www.scmp.com/news/china/society/article/1848329/no-absolute-certainty-yet-reunion-island-wing-piece-part-missing","title\u003d\u0027No absolute certainty yet\u0027 Reunion Island wing piece part of missing flight MH370","author\u003dLaura Zhou","pub\u003dSouth China Morning Post","date\u003dAugust 10, 2015"]},{"name":"source","description":["url\u003dhttp://news.sky.com/story/1533314/mh370-debris-search-spreads-to-maldives","title\u003dMH370 Debris Search Spreads To Maldives","author\u003d","pub\u003dSky News","date\u003dAugust 10, 2015"]},{"name":"source","description":["url\u003dhttp://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-33846493","title\u003dMH370: Malaysia sends experts to examine Maldives \u0027debris\u0027","author\u003d","pub\u003dBBC News Online","date\u003dAugust 10, 2015"]},{"name":"source","description":["url\u003dhttp://news.yahoo.com/malaysia-verify-debris-maldives-came-plane-105657770.html","title\u003dMalaysia to verify if debris in Maldives came from plane","author\u003d(TEMPLATE)","pub\u003dYahoo! News","date\u003dAugust 10, 2015"]},{"name":"source","description":["url\u003dhttp://www.reuters.com/article/2015/08/10/us-malaysia-airlines-crash-idUSKCN0QF0YF20150810","title\u003dMalaysia to inspect suspected plane debris found in Maldives","author\u003dAl-Zaquan Amer Hamzah and Praveen Menon","pub\u003dReuters","date\u003dAugust 10, 2015"]},{"name":"Publish","description":[]},{"name":"Archive","description":[]}],"templatesSchema":["title","date","url","title","author","pub","date","url","title","author","pub","date","url","title","auth