{"title":"Bernie Sanders embraces Black Lives Matter movement","wikiTitle":"Bernie_Sanders_embraces_Black_Lives_Matter_movement","wid":2487108,"lang":"en","namespace":"","integerNamespace":0,"timestamp":"2015-10-17T16:27:51Z","type":"ARTICLE","tables":[],"lists":[["TEMPLATE[source, url\u003d http://www.salon.com/2015/10/05/bernie_sanders_admits_he_initially_mishandled_black_lives_matter_i_plead_guilty_i_should_have_been_more_sensitive/, title\u003d Bernie Sanders admits he initially mishandled Black Lives Matter: âI plead guilty â I should have been more sensitiveâ, author\u003d Sophia Tesfaye, pub\u003dSalon (website), date\u003d October 5, 2015]","TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://www.ibtimes.com/bernie-sanders-black-lives-matter-white-americans-not-sensitive-african-american-2127789, title\u003dBernie Sanders Black Lives Matter: White Americans \u0027Not Sensitive\u0027 To African-American Struggles, Presidential Candidate Says, author\u003dAbigail Abrams, pub\u003dInternational Business Times, date\u003d October 5, 2015]","TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://time.com/3996001/bernie-sanders-black-lives-matter/, title\u003dBernie Sanders Is Wrong To Ignore âBlack Lives Matter\u0027, author\u003d Darlena Cunha, pub\u003dTime (magazine), date\u003dAugust 13, 2015]"]],"links":[{"id":"United_States","description":"United States"},{"id":"United_States_presidential_election,_2016","description":"Presidential candidate"},{"id":"Bernie_Sanders","description":"Bernie Sanders"},{"id":"Missouri","description":"Missouri"}],"externalLinks":[],"sections":["Sources"],"paragraphs":["TEMPLATE[date, October 8, 2015] TEMPLATE[2016_US_Presidential_Election] TEMPLATE[Image_credit, US Congress] United States Presidential candidate Bernie Sanders discussed his understanding of the TEMPLATE[w, Black Lives Matter, Black Lives Matter movement] on Monday.","\"Many white people are not sensitive\", Sanders noted, speaking with magazine TEMPLATE[w, Ebony (magazine), Ebony], \"to the kind of abuse that TEMPLATE[wikt, African-American, African-Americans], especially younger African-Americans, receive at the hands of police officers and police departments\".","The Black Lives Matter activist movement protests police brutality against African Americans, and gained traction after the death of TEMPLATE[w, Shooting of Michael Brown, Michael Brown] last year in TEMPLATE[w, Ferguson, Missouri, Ferguson], Missouri.","Sanders also recently admitted, speaking to magazine TEMPLATE[w, The New Yorker], that when the Black Lives Matter movement first came to light, he mishandled his dealings with them: \"I plead guilty â I should have been more sensitive at the beginning of this campaign to talk about this issue [...] The issues these young people raised are enormously important\".","Senator Sanders has had several incidents involving the group, including when they interrupted one of his rallies in TEMPLATE[w, Seattle] in August. He said talking with members of the movement has helped him understand what the movement is about.","Sanders has been strongly criticized for his previous treatment of the group, particularly when his campaign began to respond to interruption from the group by shouting \"we stand together\" repeatedly at them.","The TEMPLATE[w, US Senate, Senator] for TEMPLATE[w, Vermont] in his Ebony interview called the US criminal justice system \"broken\", saying, \"One of the ongoing crises in America is institutional racism\".","TEMPLATE[haveyoursay]","TEMPLATE[Publish] TEMPLATE[Archive]"],"categories":[{"id":"Category:Bernie_Sanders","description":"Category:Bernie Sanders"},{"id":"Category:2016_United_States_presidential_election","description":"Category:2016 United States presidential election"},{"id":"Category:United_States","description":"Category:United States"},{"id":"Category:North_America","description":"Category:North America"},{"id":"Category:Elections","description":"Category:Elections"},{"id":"Category:Politics_and_conflicts","descripti