ndash;1 against local rivals TEMPLATE[w, Everton F.C., Everton].","Klopp previously served as the manager at German football club TEMPLATE[w, Borussia Dortmund] (BVB) and won the German TEMPLATE[w, Bundesliga] with them twice. Klopp held the position of Dortmund manager until May 2015, and his last match was against TEMPLATE[w, VfL Wolfsburg, Wolfsburg] in the TEMPLATE[w, DFB Pokal] cup.","This signing made Klopp the highest-paid manager in Liverpool history. His first match in the Premier League will be against TEMPLATE[w, Tottenham Hotspur] on October 17. Liverpool have only had four wins out of eleven league games this season.","In response to this signing, Borussia Dortmund tweeted \"We heard the news today, oh boy! All the best at the Kop, JÃ¼rgen Klopp!\"","TEMPLATE[haveyoursay]","TEMPLATE[Publish] TEMPLATE[Archive]","CAT:Football (soccer) CAT:Sports CAT:Liverpool CAT:England CAT:Germany CAT:Liverpool F.C."],"categories":[{"id":"Category:Culture_and_entertainment","description":"Category:Culture and entertainment"},{"id":"Category:Borussia_Dortmund","description":"Category:Borussia Dortmund"}],"templates":[{"name":"date","description":["October 10, 2015"]},{"name":"Audio_box_2","description":["filename\u003dJÃ¼rgen Klopp signs 3 year contract with Liverpool audio wikinews.wav","text\u003dListen to this article","date\u003d2015-10-11"]},{"name":"Liverpool","description":[]},{"name":"w","description":["Liverpool F.C."]},{"name":"w","description":["JÃ¼rgen Klopp"]},{"name":"w","description":["Pound sterling","GBP Â£"]},{"name":"w","description":["Premier League"]},{"name":"w","description":["UEFA Champions League"]},{"name":"w","description":["Brendan Rodgers"]},{"name":"w","description":["Anfield"]},{"name":"w","description":["Tie (draw)#Association football","drew"]},{"name":"w","description":["Everton F.C.","Everton"]},{"name":"w","description":["Borussia Dortmund"]},{"name":"w","description":["Bundesliga"]},{"name":"w","description":["VfL Wolfsburg","Wolfsbur