{"title":"Israelis killed, injured in Jerusalem bus attack; wave of violence continues","wikiTitle":"Israelis_killed,_injured_in_Jerusalem_bus_attack;_wave_of_violence_continues","wid":2504968,"lang":"en","namespace":"","integerNamespace":0,"timestamp":"2015-10-22T20:30:07Z","type":"ARTICLE","tables":[],"lists":[["TEMPLATE[source, url\u003d http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-34513753, title\u003d Three Israelis killed in Jerusalem attacks, pub\u003d BBC News Online, date\u003d October 13, 2015]"],["TEMPLATE[source, url\u003d http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/10/13/us-israel-palestinians-violence-idUSKCN0S70ML20151013, title\u003d Two killed in Palestinian \u0027Day of Rage\u0027 attacks: police, author\u003d Jeffrey Heller, pub\u003d Reuters, date\u003d October 13, 2015]"],["TEMPLATE[source, url\u003d http://www.timesrepublican.com/page/content.detail/id/947231/Q-A--No-end-in-sight-for-latest-Israeli-Palestinian-violence.html?isap\u003d1\u0026nav\u003d5015, title\u003d Q\u0026A: No end in sight for latest Israeli-Palestinian violence, author\u003d (TEMPLATE), pub\u003d Times-Republican, date\u003d October 12, 2015]"]],"links":[{"id":"Israel","description":"Israel"},{"id":"Jerusalem","description":"Jerusalem"},{"id":"Palestine","description":"Palestinians"},{"id":"Palestinian_National_Authority","description":"Palestinian National Authority"},{"id":"West_Bank","description":"West Bank"}],"externalLinks":[],"sections":["Sources"],"paragraphs":["TEMPLATE[date, October 13, 2015] TEMPLATE[Audio_box_2, filename\u003dIsraelis killed, injured in Jerusalem bus attack; wave of violence continues audio wikinews.wav, text\u003dListen to this article, date\u003d2015-10-14] TEMPLATE[palestine] Today, two Israelis were reported killed and several injured as a result of an attack on a bus in Jerusalem. This is one of several violent occurrences from today, as part of a recent surge of violence in the region.","The Israeli police stated that in the attack on the bus in Jerusalem, the two Palestinian assailants opened fire and also stabbed passengers on the bus. Israeli forces arrived at the location and neutralized the attackers, one of whom was killed.","Also today, several other attacks on Israeli territory, committed by Palestinians, have been reported. One Israeli citizen was killed and more were injured during knife and vehicle attacks in major Israeli cities including Jerusalem and TEMPLATE[w, Raanana]. In most cases the assailants were shot down or otherwise neutralized by Israeli security forces or citizens.","These events follow an extended surge of violence afflicting Israel and the Palestinian National Authority this past month. The violence spreading through Israel and the West Bank originated from tensions over a holy site in Jerusalem. So far 30 Palestinians have been reported killed and hundreds wounded during recent events, whereas eight Israelis have been reported killed and dozens wounded.","TEMPLATE[haveyoursay]","TEMPLATE[Publish] TEMPLATE[Archive]"],"categories":[{"id":"Category:Middle_East","description":"Category:Middle East"},{"id":"Category:Politics_and_conflicts","description":"Category:Politics and conflicts"},{"id":"Category:Palestine","description":"Category:Palestine"},{"id":"Category:Israel","description":"Category:Israel"},{"id":"Category:Israel/Palestine_Conflict","description":"Category:Israel/Palestine Conflict"},{"id":"Category:Jerusalem","description":"Category:Jerusalem"},{"id":"Category:West_Bank","description":"Category:West Bank"},{"id":"Category:Crime_and_law","description":"Category:Crime and law"}],"templates":[{"name":"date","description":["October 13, 2015"]},{"name":"Audio_box_2","description":["filename\u003dIsraelis killed, injured in Jerusalem bus attack; wave of violence continues audio wikinews.wav","text\u003dListen to this article","date\u003d2015-10-14"]},{"name":"palestine","description":[]},{"name":"w","description":["Raanana"]},{"name":"haveyoursay","description":[]},{"name":"source","description":["url\u003d http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-34513753","title\u003d Three Israelis killed in Jerusalem attacks","pub\u003d BBC News Online","date\u003d October 13, 2015"]},{"name":"source","description":["url\u003d http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/10/13/us-israel-palestinians-violence-idUSKCN0S70ML20151013","title\u003d Two killed in Palestinian \u0027Day of Rage\u0027 attacks: police","author\u003d Jeffrey Heller","pub\u003d Reuters","date\u003d October 13, 2015"]},{"name":"source","description":["url\u003d http://www.timesrepublican.com/page/content.detail/id/947231/Q-A--No-end-in-sight-for-latest-Israeli-Palestinian-violence.html?isap\u003d1\u0026nav\u003d5015","title\u003d Q\u0026A: No end in sight for latest Israeli-Palestinian violence","author\u003d (TEMPLATE)","pub\u003d Times-Republican","date\u003d October 12, 2015"]},{"name":"Publish","description":[]},{"name":"Archive","description":[]}],"templatesSchema":["filename","text","date","url","title","pub","date","url","title","author","pub","date","url","title","author","pub","date"],"highlights":[]}
{"title":"Netherlands out of Euro 2016 as van Persie scores own goal against Czech Republic","wikiTitle":"Netherlands_out_of_Euro_2016_as_van_Persie_scores_own_goal_against_Czech_Republic","wid":2505571,"lang":"en","namespace":"","integerNamespace":0,"timestamp":"2016-11-08T04:09:54Z","type":"ARTICLE","tables":[{"name":"","table":[["Position !! Team !! P !! W !! D !! L !! F !! A !! +/- !! Pts"],["1"," Czech Republic","10","7","1","2","19","14","5","22"],["2"," Iceland","10","6","2","2","17","6","11","20"],["3"," Turkey","10","5","3","2","14","9","5","18"],["4"," The Netherlands","10","4","1","5","17","14","3","13"],["5"," Kazakhstan","10","1","2","7","7","18","-11","5"],["6"," Latvia","10","0","5","5","6","19","-13","5"]],"numCols":10,"numRows":7}],"lists":[["TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://www.uefa.com/uefaeuro/qualifiers/season\u003d2016/standings/round\u003d2000446/group\u003d2002428/index.html, title\u003dEuropean Qualifiers - Standings - UEFA.com, author\u003d, pub\u003dUEFA.com, date\u003dOctober 14, 2015]","TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/33544119, title\u003dNetherlands 2-3 Czech Republic, date\u003dOctober 13, 2015, pub\u003dBBC Sport, author\u003d]","TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://www.theguardian.com/football/live/2015/oct/13/turkey-v-iceland-and-holland-on-the-brink-euro-2016-qualifiers-clockwatch-live, title\u003dEuro 2016 qualifiers clockwatch â as it happened, author\u003dScott Murray, pub\u003dThe Guardian, date\u003dOctober 13, 2015]"]],"links":[{"id":"football_(soccer)","description":"football"},{"id":"Netherlands","description":"Dutch"}],"externalLinks":[],"sections":["Match stats","Sister link","Sources"],"paragraphs":["TEMPLATE[date, October 14, 2015] TEMPLATE[Audio_box_2, filename\u003dNetherlands out of Euro 16 as van Persie scores own goal against Czech Republic Audio Wikinews.wav, text\u003dListen to this article, date\u003d2015-10-14] TEMPLATE[football] Yesterday, the TEMPLATE[w, Netherlands national football team, Netherlands] football team crashed out of the TEMPLATE[w, UEFA European Championship, UEFA Euro Cup] TEMPLATE[w, UEFA Euro 2016, 2016] after a 2\u0026ndash;3 defeat against the TEMPLATE[w, Czech Republic national football team, Czech Republic] in TEMPLATE[w, UEFA Euro 2016 qualifying, a qualifying match]. Dutch player TEMPLATE[w, Robin van Persie] scored an own goal.","The match was held in the TEMPLATE[w, Amsterdam ArenA] in the Dutch capital. TEMPLATE[w, Turkey national football team, Turkey], TEMPLATE[w, Iceland national football team, Iceland] and the Czech Republic qualified for the tournament from group A, Turkey defeating Iceland 1\u0026ndash;0 to take third position.","The Dutch team, nicknamed Oranje, had 60% ball possession in front of the Czechs. The match saw six TEMPLATE[w, yellow card (association football), yellow cards] and one TEMPLATE[w, red card (association football), red card]. Four Dutch players were shown yellow cards.  A total of 30 fouls were committed in the match, seventeen by the Dutch, and thirteen by the Czechs. Czech defender TEMPLATE[w, Marek SuchÃ½, SuchÃ½] was sent off in the 43rd minute.","The first half saw two goals by the visitors, three yellow cards, and one red card. The first goal came in the 24th minute. TEMPLATE[w, Pavel KaderÃ¡bek, KaderÃ¡bek], TEMPLATE[w, Assist (football), assisted] by TEMPLATE[w, JiÅÃ­ SkalÃ¡k, SkalÃ¡k], scored. TEMPLATE[w, TomÃ¡Å¡ Necid] assisted for the second goal, TEMPLATE[w, Josef Å ural] scoring in the bottom left corner.","In the second half, Robin van Persie scored an TEMPLATE[w, own goal] in the 66th minute, providing the visitors a 3\u0026ndash;0 lead. The Dutch side won a corner in the 70th minute, from which TEMPLATE[w, Klaas-Jan Huntelaar] reduced the goal difference with a header, assisted by TEMPLATE[w, Wesley Sneijder].","Later, in the 83rd minute, van Persie scored in the correct net, making it 2\u0026ndash;3 for the Netherlands, assisted by TEMPLATE[w, Bas Dost]. In the next minute, van Persie was booked for TEMPLATE[w, Diving (association football), diving].","The match ended in a 2\u0026ndash;3 loss for the Oranje, and they failed to qualify for the Euros for the first time since 1984. In order to qualify, the Dutch had to beat the Czechs and rely on Iceland to beat Turkey. A ten-man Turkish side defeated Iceland 1\u0026ndash;0 and qualified for the tournament. Group A standings","TEMPLATE[haveyoursay]TEMPLATE[clear]","TEMPLATE[footballbox, date\u003d, team1\u003d (TEMPLATE) [[File:Flag of the Netherlands.svg, 30px]], score\u003d 2 â 3, team2\u003d [[File:Flag of the Czech Republic.svg, 30px]] (TEMPLATE), goals1\u003d  (TEMPLATE) (TEMPLATE) (TEMPLATE)\u003cbr\u003e (TEMPLATE) (TEMPLATE) (TEMPLATE)\u003cbr\u003e(TEMPLATE) (TEMPLATE)\u003cbr\u003e(TEMPLATE) (TEMPLATE), goals2\u003d (TEMPLATE) (TEMPLATE)\u003cbr\u003e(TEMPLATE) (TEMPLATE)\u003cbr\u003e(TEMPLATE) (TEMPLATE)\u003cbr\u003e(TEMPLATE) (TEMPLATE)\u003cbr\u003e(TEMPLATE) (TEMPLATE)\u003cbr\u003e(TEMPLATE) (TEMPLATE), stadium\u003d (TEMPLATE), (TEMPLATE), referee\u003d (TEMPLATE), (TEMPLATE)]","TEMPLATE[donut, team1-size\u003d60, team2-size\u003d3, team1-pos\u003d60, team2-pos\u003d40, bg\u003d#ff4f00, deg1\u003d270, deg2\u003d54, wdeg1\u003d-144, wdeg2\u003d0, team1-color\u003d#ff4f00, team2-color\u003d#fff, team1\u003dThe Netherlands, team2\u003dCzech Republic]    TEMPLATE[Football_stat, stat-name\u003dShots, team1-stat1-percent-into-1000-without-px\u003d520, team1-jersey-color\u003d#f40, team1-text\u003d#fff, team1-stat-value\u003d13, team2-stat-value\u003d12, team2-text\u003d#000, team2-jersey-color\u003d(TEMPLATE), team2-stat2-percent-into-1000-without-px\u003d480] TEMPLATE[Football_stat, stat-name\u003dShots on target, team1-stat1-percent-into-1000-without-px\u003d571.4, team1-jersey-color\u003d#f40, team1-text\u003d#fff, team1-stat-value\u003d4, team2-stat-value\u003d3, team2-text\u003d#000, team2-jersey-color\u003d(TEMPLATE), team2-stat2-percent-into-1000-without-px\u0