uguese footballer TEMPLATE[w, Cristiano Ronaldo] surpassed TEMPLATE[w, RaÃºl (footballer), RaÃºl]\u0027s goal scoring record for Spanish club Real Madrid in a La Liga match against TEMPLATE[w, Levante UD] on Saturday. Ronaldo netted his 324th goal in his 310th match for Los Blancos on Saturday, breaking the  previous record set by Spanish footballer RaÃºl of 323 goals in 741 games.","He earlier equaled RaÃºl\u0027s goal scoring record for Madrid in a TEMPLATE[w, UEFA Champions League] match against Swedish football club TEMPLATE[w, MalmÃ¶ FF] when he scored a brace, crossing the landmark of 500 career goals and scored the record-breaking goal in the 30th minute from outside the TEMPLATE[w, penalty area] in this match.","In Saturday\u0027s match, Real Madrid had 58% ball possession against Levante. The match saw five TEMPLATE[w, yellow card (association football), yellow cards]\u0026nbsp;\u0026mdash; four for the visitors and one for Real Madrid player TEMPLATE[w, Mateo KovaÄiÄ, KovaÄiÄ]. A total of eighteen fouls were committed in the game. Ronaldo TEMPLATE[w, Assist (football), assisted] Brazilian TEMPLATE[w, Marcelo Vieira, Marcelo] in the 27th minute and Marcelo netted the goal in the left corner. Minutes later, TEMPLATE[w, Toni Kroos] assisted Ronaldo, and he scored the record-breaking goal in the bottom right corner. The first half ended 2\u0026ndash;0.","At the beginning of the second half, TEMPLATE[w, Lucas VÃ¡zquez, VÃ¡zquez] was substituted for TEMPLATE[w, Gareth Bale]. He assisted TEMPLATE[w, JesÃ©] in the 81st minute and JesÃ© scored in the top corner providing a 3\u0026ndash;0 win for Real Madrid.","Real is now top of the La Liga table.  TEMPLATE[q, What Ronaldo does you cannot name. It is on another historic level,[...]It is incredible what he has done in only six years, scoring an average of more than 50 goals a season, when it used to be hard for me to reach 20. I hope he keeps scoring many more goals for a long time and helps the team to win titl