{"title":"Nico Rosberg takes pole for 2015 Brazilian Grand Prix","wikiTitle":"Nico_Rosberg_takes_pole_for_2015_Brazilian_Grand_Prix","wid":2580067,"lang":"en","namespace":"","integerNamespace":0,"timestamp":"2015-11-25T21:58:27Z","type":"ARTICLE","tables":[],"lists":[["TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://www.motorsport.com/f1/news/brazilian-gp-rosberg-beats-hamilton-to-grab-fifth-straight-pole/, title\u003dBrazilian GP: Rosberg beats Hamilton to grab fifth straight pole, author\u003dPablo Elizalde, pub\u003dmotorsport.com, date\u003dNovember 14, 2015]","TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/121799, title\u003dBrazilian GP: Nico Rosberg extends F1 pole streak at Interlagos, author\u003dBen Anderson, pub\u003dAutosport, date\u003dNovember 14, 2015]"]],"links":[{"id":"Nico_Rosberg","description":"Nico Rosberg"},{"id":"Lewis_Hamilton","description":"Lewis Hamilton"},{"id":"Nico_Hulkenberg","description":"Nico Hulkenberg"},{"id":"Daniil_Kvyat","description":"Daniil Kvyat"},{"id":"Daniel_Ricciardo","description":"Daniel Ricciardo"}],"externalLinks":[],"sections":["Sources"],"paragraphs":["TEMPLATE[date, November 14, 2015] TEMPLATE[sports] TEMPLATE[w, Mercedes-Benz, Mercedes] driver Nico Rosberg today took pole position for tomorrow\u0027s 2015 TEMPLATE[w, Brazilian Grand Prix] at TEMPLATE[w, Interlagos], making it his fifth pole in a row. Lewis Hamilton was second fastest. Four-time world champion TEMPLATE[w, Sebastian Vettel] rounded up the top three.","TEMPLATE[w, Germany, German] driver Rosberg lapped the track at the TEMPLATE[w, AutÃ³dromo JosÃ© Carlos Pace] in TEMPLATE[w, Sao Paulo] in 1:11.282.","His teammate Lewis Hamilton was second fastest, a mere .078 of a second slower. Despite being faster in the earlier parts of qualifying, the newly crowned world champion couldn\u0027t beat his teammate on the third qualifying lap.","Sebastian Vettel took third spot for TEMPLATE[w, Ferrari], lapping four tenths of a second slower than the Mercedes cars.","TEMPLATE[w, Williams Grand Prix Engineering, Williams]\u0027s TEMPLATE[w, Valtteri Bottas] took fourth place with a time of 1:12.085. He isn\u0027t to start in fourth place though, as he faces a three place grid penalty following an incident during free practice.","Fellow TEMPLATE[w, Finland, Finn] TEMPLATE[w, Kimi RÃ¤ikkÃ¶nen] in the second TEMPLATE[w, Ferrari] was in fifth place. As a result of his countryman\u0027s penalty he is to start in fourth place after his teammate. TEMPLATE[w, Force India]\u0027s Nico Hulkenberg set the sixth fastest time of the session, while TEMPLATE[w, Red Bull] drivers Daniil Kvyat and Daniel Ricciardo finished seventh and ninth respectively.","TEMPLATE[w, Australia, Australian] Ricciardo also faced a grid penalty, as an engine change causes him to start tomorrow\u0027s race ten places further back. Eighth place went to local hero TEMPLATE[w, Felipe Massa] in his Williams. Eighteen-year-old TEMPLATE[w, Scuderia Toro Rosso, Toro Rosso] driver TEMPLATE[w, Max Verstappen] finished in an impressive tenth position.","TEMPLATE[haveyoursay]","TEMPLATE[Publish] TEMPLATE[Archive]"],"categories":[{"id":"Category:Sports","description":"Category:Sports"},{"id":"Category:Auto_racing","description":"Category:Auto racing"},{"id":"Category:Nico_Rosberg","description":"Category:Nico Rosberg"},{"id":"Category:Lewis_Hamilton","description":"Category:Lewis Hamilton"},{"id":"Category:Brazil","description":"Category:Brazil"},{"id":"Category:South_America","description":"Category:South America"},{"id":"Category:Formula_One","description":"Category:Formula One"},{"id":"Category:Nico_HÃ¼lkenberg","description":"Category:Nico HÃ¼lkenberg"},{"id":"Category:Daniil_Kvyat","description":"Category:Daniil Kvyat"},{"id":"Category:Daniel_Ricciardo","description":"Category:Daniel Ricciardo"}],"templates":[{"name":"date","description":["November 14, 2015"]},{"name":"sports","description":[]},{"name":"w","description":["Mercedes-Benz","Mercedes"]},{"name":"w","