{"title":"UK\u0027s \u0027ban Trump\u0027 petition passes half-million mark","wikiTitle":"UK\u0027s_\u0027ban_Trump\u0027_petition_passes_half-million_mark","wid":2647577,"lang":"en","namespace":"","integerNamespace":0,"timestamp":"2015-12-22T21:11:30Z","type":"ARTICLE","tables":[],"lists":[["TEMPLATE[wikinews, title\u003dPetition calls for Trump UK ban, date\u003dDecember 9, 2015]"],["TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://www.independent.ie/world-news/europe/half-a-million-sign-online-petition-to-ban-mogul-entering-uk-34280916.html, title\u003dHalf a million sign online petition to ban mogul entering UK, author\u003dDean Gray, pub\u003dIrish Independent, date\u003dDecember 12, 2015]","TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://www.jpost.com/Not-Just-News/Activists-petition-NASA-Dump-Trump-into-outer-space-437104, title\u003dActivists petition NASA: Dump Trump into outer space, author\u003d, pub\u003dThe Jerusalem Post, date\u003dDecember 12, 2015]","TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://www.nbcnews.com/news/world/petition-ban-trump-u-k-most-popular-ever-government-site-n478031?cid\u003dpar-time_20151211, title\u003dPetition to Ban Trump From U.K. Is Most Popular Ever on Government Site, author\u003dPhil Helsel, pub\u003dNBC News, date\u003dDecember 11, 2015]","TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2015/dec/09/donald-trump-petition-ban-from-uk-suzanne-kelly-shocked-strong-support, title\u003dWoman behind petition to ban Donald Trump from UK âshockedâ by support, author\u003d, pub\u003dThe Guardian, date\u003dDecember 9, 2015]","TEMPLATE[source, url\u003dhttp://www.nytimes.com/2015/12/09/world/europe/donald-trumps-call-to-bar-muslims-reverberates-abroad.html?_r\u003d0, title\u003dTrumpâs Plan to Bar Muslims Is Widely Condemned Abroad, author\u003dDan Bilefsky, pub\u003dThe New York Times, date\u003dDecember 8, 2015]"],["Block Donald J Trump from UK entry \u0026mdash; UK Government Petition site","Petition to send Donald Trump into Space and Leave Him There. \u0026mdash; Change.org","House of Commons recess dates \u0026mdash; UK Parliament website"]],"links":[],"externalLinks":[{"id":"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/114003","description":"Block Donald J Trump from UK entry"},{"id":"https://www.change.org/p/nasa-petition-to-send-donald-trump-into-space-and-leave-him-there","description":"Petition to send Donald Trump into Space and Leave Him There."},{"id":"http://www.parliament.uk/about/faqs/house-of-commons-faqs/business-faq-page/recess-dates/","description":"House of Commons recess dates"}],"sections":["Related news","Sources","External links"],"paragraphs":["TEMPLATE[date, December 12, 2015]TEMPLATE[2016_US_Presidential_Election] TEMPLATE[w, Donald Trump]TEMPLATE[image_credit, Gage Skidmore] A petition on the TEMPLATE[w, UK] government\u0027s website, calling for TEMPLATE[w, US] Presidential hopeful TEMPLATE[w, Donald Trump] to be barred from entering the country, has now passed a half-million signatories becoming the most-popular petition ever posted on the site. The signatories include a majority of UK TEMPLATE[w, Member of parliament, MPs].","The petition was originally submitted late November by campaigner Suzanne Kelly from TEMPLATE[w, Aberdeen], preceding Trump\u0027s remarks which prompted the overwhelming response. Kelly, saying her attention was drawn due to concerns over Trump\u0027s golfing developments in the area, noted, \"I never in my wildest dreams imagined it would get so many signatures\". Locally, TEMPLATE[w, Robert Gordon University] have stripped an honorary degree from Trump, and First Minister TEMPLATE[w, Nicola Sturgeon] removed him from the GlobalScot network of business ambassadors.","Following the tycoon\u0027s call for a \"complete shutdown of TEMPLATE[w, Islam, Muslims] entering the United States\", an TEMPLATE[w, NBC]/TEMPLATE[w, The Wall Street Journal, WSJ] survey found the majority of adults in the United States disagree with him. The remarks also prompted global criticism of Trump.","TEMPLATE[w, London] mayor TEMPLATE[w, Boris Johnson] said the demand made him \"unfit to hold the office of the president of the United States\". TEMPLATE[w, France, French] Prime minister TEMPLATE[w, Manuel Valls] stated on TEMPLATE[w, Twitter], \"Mr. Trump, like others, fuels hatred [...] our only enemy is radical TEMPLATE[w, Islamism].\" The director of the American university in TEMPLATE[w, Cairo]\u0027s TEMPLATE[w, Kamal Adham Center for Television and Digital Journalism], TEMPLATE[w, Hafez Al Mirazi], said: \"What we are getting now is really terrible [...] Stuff that only the TEMPLATE[w, Ku Klux Klan] and others would say.\" Kassem Allie, from the TEMPLATE[w, Islamic Center of America], accused Trump of evoking fear \"reminiscent of TEMPLATE[w, Nazi Germany, Nazi Germany]\".","In contrast, a humorous petition calling on TEMPLATE[w, NASA] to \"send Donald Trump into Space and Leave Him There\"  on the change.org site has exceeded 30,000 signatures. Autumn Boehle from TEMPLATE[w, Michigan], who started the petition last Wednesday, says, if the petition garners sufficient signatures, she will provide a link where people can: \"donate to make this happen. It wont be cheap, but it will be worth while.\"","The petition to ban Donald Trump from the UK, having passed 100,000 signatures, is now eligible for debate in the TEMPLATE[w, UK House of Commons, House of Commons].","TEMPLATE[haveyoursay]","TEMPLATE[Original]","TEMPLATE[Publish] TEMPLATE[Archive]"],"categories":[{"id":"Category:United_Kingdom","description":"Category:United Kingdom"},{"id":"Category:Politics_and_conflicts","description":"Category:Politics and conflicts"},{"id":"Category:United_States","description":"Category:United States"},{"id":"Category:Boris_Johnson","description":"Category:Boris Johnson"},{"id":"Category:Donald_Trump","description":"Category:Donald Trump"},{"id":"Category:Nicola_Sturgeon","description":"Category:Nicola Sturgeon"},{"id":"Category:Europe","description":"Category:Europe"},{"id":"Category:North_America","description":"Category:North America"},{"id":"Category:Brian_McNeil_(Wikinewsie)","description":"Category:Brian McNeil (Wikinewsie)"}],"templates":[{"name":"date","description":["December 12, 2015"]},{"name":"2016_US_Presidential_Election","description":[]},{"name":"w","description":["Donald Trump"]},{"name":"image_credit","description":["Gage Skidmore"]},{"name":"w","description":["UK"]},{"name":"w","description":["US"]},{"name":"w","description":["Donald Trump"]},{"name":"w","description":["Member of parliament","MPs"]},{"name":"w","description":["Aberdeen"]},{"name":"w","description":["Robert Gordon University"]},{"name":"w","description":["Nicola Sturgeon"]},{"name":"w","description":["Islam","Muslims"]},{"name":"w","description":["NBC"]},{"name":"w","description":["The Wall Street Journal","WSJ"]},{"name":"w","description":["London"]},{"name":"w","description":["Boris Johnson"]},{"name":"w","description":["France","French"]},{"name":"w","description":["Manuel Valls"]},{"name":"w","description":["Twitter"]},{"name":"w","description":["Islamism"]},{"name":"w","description":["Cairo"]},{"name":"w","description":["Kamal Adham Center for Television and Digital Journalism"]},{"name":"w","description":["Hafez Al Mirazi"]},{"name":"w","description":["Ku Klux Klan"]},{"name":"w","description":["Islamic Center of America"]},{"name":"w","description":["Nazi Germany","Nazi Germany"]},{"name":"w","description":["NASA"]},{"name":"w","description":["Michigan"]},{"name":"w","description":["UK House of Commons","House of Commons"]},{"name":"haveyoursay","description":[]},{"name":"wikinews","description":["title\u003dPetition calls for Trump UK ban","date\u003dDecember 9, 2015"]},{"name":"Original","description":[]},{"name":"source","description":["url\u003dhttp://www.independent.ie/world-news/europe/half-a-million-sign-online-petition-to-ban-mogul-entering-uk-34280916.html","title\u003dHalf a million sign online petition to ban mogul entering UK","author\u003dDean Gray","pub\u003dIrish Independent","date\u003dDecember 12, 2015"]},{"name":"source","description":["url\u003dhttp://www.jpost.com/Not-Just-News/Activists-petition-NASA-Dump-Trump-into-outer-space-437104","title\u003dActivists petition NASA: Dump Trump into outer space","author\u003d","pub\u003dThe Jerusalem Post","date\u003dDecember 12, 2015"]},{"name":"source","description":["url\u003dhttp://www.nbcnews.com/news/world/petition-ban-trump-u-k-most-popular-ever-government-site-n478031?cid\u003dpar-time_20151211","title\u003dPetition to Ban Trump From U.K. Is Most Popular Ever on Government Site","author\u003dPhil Helsel","pub\u003dNBC News","date\u003dDecember 11, 2015"]},{"name":"source","description":["url\u003dhttp://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2015/dec/09/donald-trump-petition-ban-from-uk-suzanne-kelly-shocked-strong-support","title\u003dWoman behind petition to ban Donald Trump from UK âshockedâ by support","author\u003d","pub\u003dThe Guardian","date\u003dDecember 9, 2015"]},{"name":"source","description":["url\u003dhttp://www.nytimes.com/2015/12/09/world/europe/donald-trumps-call-to-bar-muslims-reverberates-abroad.html?_r\u003d0","title\u003dTrumpâs Plan to Bar Muslims Is Widely Condemned Abroad","author\u003dDan Bilefsky","pub\u003dThe New York Times","date\u003dDecember 8, 2015"]},{"name":"Publish","description":[]},{"name":"Archive","description":[]}],"templatesSchema":["title","date","url","title","author","pub","date","url","title","author","pub","date","url","title","author","pub","date","url","title","author","pub","date","url","title","author","pub","date"],"highlights":[]}
